All Implemented Interfaces:
Runnable
public class ArrayWayOverlay
extends WayOverlay<OverlayWay>

ArrayWayOverlay is a thread-safe implementation of the WayOverlay class using an ArrayList as internal data structure. Default paints for all OverlayWays without individual paints can be defined via the constructor.
